      • compareTo

        public int compareTo​(Power o)
        This method is used to implement the comparable interface by comparing the date recorded of the power recording. This method is called from a power object, and compares to another power object in the parameter.
        Specified by:
        compareTo in interface java.lang.Comparable<Power>
        Parameters:
        o - The object 'o' is of type Power.
        Returns:
        This method returns 0 if the two were recorded on the same date, -1 if the calling Power object was recorded prior to the parameter object and 1 if the calling Power object was recorded after the paramater object.
